```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    actor user
    participant browser
    participant server

    user->>browser: inputs note
    activate browser
    browser->>browser: redraws list of notes
    deactivate browser 
    browser->>server: HTTP POST /new_note_spa
    activate server 
    note right of browser: Content-type: application/json    
    server-->>browser: HTTP 201 code
    deactivate server    
    note left of browser: browser shows updated list of notes
    browser-->>user: lists notes
```